{"parse":{"title":"Allard's Law/de","pageid":2944,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>2-1-265</b>\n</p><p><big><big><big>Tragweitenformel\n</big></big></big></p><p><big><big><big>Allardsche Formel</big></big></big>\n</p><p>Gleichung, die den Zusammenhang zwischen der Lichtst\u00e4rke einer punktf\u00f6rmigen Lichtquelle und der von ihr in vorgegebenem Abstand auf einer Fl\u00e4che senkrecht zur Lichteinfallsrichtung erzeugten Beleuchtungsst\u00e4rke unter Ber\u00fccksichtigung der Lichtdurchl\u00e4ssigkeit der als homogen angenommenen Atmosph\u00e4re beschreibt.\n</p><p>Die Gleichung kann wie folgt geschrieben werden:\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Allard1.gif\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/1/1c/Allard1.gif\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"71\" height=\"45\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span>\n</p><p>Hierin bedeuten:\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"3a3ea00cfc35332cedf6e5e9a32e94da\">E</span>  Beleuchtungsst\u00e4rke auf der Fl\u00e4che\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"dd7536794b63bf90eccfd37f9b147d7f\">I</span>  Lichtst\u00e4rke des einfallenden Lichtes in Me\u00dfrichtung\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"b9ece18c950afbfa6b0fdbfa4ff731d3\">T</span>  atmosph\u00e4rischer Durchl\u00e4ssigkeitsfaktor der als homogen angenommenen Atmosph\u00e4re, bezogen auf eine bestimmte L\u00e4ngeneinheit\n</p><p>x  Abstand der Fl\u00e4che von der Lichtquelle in bestimmten L\u00e4ngeneinheiten. \n</p><p><br>\nAnmerkung:\n</p><p>Die Tragweitenformel kann auch wie folgt geschrieben werden:\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Allard2.gif\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/d/db/Allard2.gif\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"96\" height=\"42\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span>\n</p><p>Hierin ist <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"5206560a306a2e085a437fd258eb57ce\">V</span> die meteorologische Sichtweite (2-1-280 und 2-1-290 Anmerkung). \n</p><p><br>\n</p><p><br>\n<br>\n<i>Please note that this is the term as it stands in the original <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> Dictionary edition (1970-1989)</i>\n<br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/Allard%27s_Law\" title=\"Allard's Law\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n\u00a0\u2022\u00a0<span lang=\"de\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Deutsch</a></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"3a3ea00cfc35332cedf6e5e9a32e94da\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Illuminance\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Energy\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"dd7536794b63bf90eccfd37f9b147d7f\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>charge current\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Intensity\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"b9ece18c950afbfa6b0fdbfa4ff731d3\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Time period\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>roll period\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Transmissivity\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"5206560a306a2e085a437fd258eb57ce\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Volume\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Volt\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Visibility\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Association of Marine Aids to Navigation and Lighthouse Authorities - AISM\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260630040547\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.060 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.068 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 69/1000000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 960/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 194/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 3/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   16.096      1 -total\n 77.08%   12.406      1 Template:Languages\n 52.21%    8.404      4 Template:Languages